# Changelog

## Features

- Plugin system for launch and shortcut creation plugins
  - Documentation: https://github.com/ActivityLauncher/ActivityLauncher/blob/feat/package-cache/PLUGIN_ARCHITECTURE.md
  - Example plugin: https://github.com/ActivityLauncher/ActivityLauncherShizukuPlugin
- Launch favorites using Quick Settings tile by @khaled-0
- Favorites and recently used activities
- Sharing of shortcuts via URL
- In-app reviews
- Translation updates

## Fixes

- App crashes when rotated
- Incremental loading should fix crashes due to binder buffer exhaustion

## Other improvements/changes

- Package cache: Further improved startup time by caching package information in SQL database
- Improved startup time: Loading of all packages skipped when opening favorites or recents
